					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"If Hotori was here she’d probably devour the thing, with hopes to melt her fat away. And with that random thought, I take a bite of my own crepe.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
